lastfm.summary: Despite having a classic nostalgic theme in the lyrics about "the good old days" this is one of The Strokes most upbeat and positive songs. The music video for the song features The Strokes at a bar having fun, as well as a game of the American game show "Family Feud" played between the Strokes and the legendary indie rock act Guided by Voices. "See, alone we stand, together we fall apart. Yeah, I think I'll be alright. I'm working so I won't have to try so hard. Tables, they turn sometimes. Oh, someday..." Read more on Last.fm.
